S.FORM: Elug sbiyaw Patungkwan ksun ga, ida bnegrahan pusu bi mndudul empsaping Ukwangryang hngkwasan Cingkwangsyu siida, elung nii ga kiya ka lmutuc hruan hidaw ni gqian hidaw. Siida lmpax djima sqlangan alang, ratac dha seusa alang ddgiyaq qmburang seejiq tnealang, mksiyaw eyyayung Cingsweysi ni msteetu 99 btunux qqahan, ida prjingan bi elug sbiyaw ka hini. "tgkingal alang brah ddgiyaq" ptasan btunux, kiya ka pqita endaan siida. Wada ta qtaan nii o hngkawas 87 siida, ida mnuru smalu nniqan sbiyaw, saan bi tmalang ni pleelug hiyi mrbu seejiq tnealang hini ka Beygi Cingsngting .

Elog sbiyaw Patongkwan kson ga, ida bnegrahan poso bi mndodol empsaping Ukwangryang hngkwasan Cingkwangsyo siida, elong nii ga kiya ka lmotoc hroan hidaw ni gqian hidaw. Siida lmpax djima sqlangan alang, ratac dha seosa alang ddgiyaq qmborang seejiq tnealang, mksiyaw eyyayong Cingsweysi ni msteeto 99 btonox qqahan, ida prjingan bi elog sbiyaw ka hini. "tgkingal alang brah ddgiyaq" ptasan btonox, kiya ka pqita endaan siida. Wada ta qtaan nii o hngkawas 87 siida, ida mnoro smalo nniqan sbiyaw, saan bi tmalang ni pleelog hiyi mrbo seejiq tnealang hini ka Beygi Cingsngting .
